                                                    Materion Corporation Conference Call Scheduled
                                                


                                                    Business Wire – 
                                                    9:07 AM ET 07/14/2017
                                                


Materion Corporation (MTRN) will hold its quarterly conference call on Thursday, July 27, 2017, at 9:00 a.m. Eastern Time to review second quarter 2017 results.

















                                                    Materion Introduces Thermalox® V Advanced Beryllium Oxide Ceramic
                                                


                                                    Business Wire – 
                                                    8:55 AM ET 06/07/2017
                                                


Advanced Materials Company Expands its BeO Ceramics Product Line Materion Corporation (MTRN) recently introduced Thermalox® V to augment its product line of advanced beryllium oxide ceramic materials.

















                                                    BRIEF-Materion, beryllium hydroxide customer complete long-term supply agreement
                                                


                                                    Reuters – 
                                                    11:47 AM ET 05/16/2017
                                                


Materion Corp (MTRN): * Materion (MTRN) and longstanding beryllium hydroxide customer complete long-term supply agreement. * Specific terms of agreement were not disclosed. * Shipments from Materion's (MTRN) mine and mill operations in Western Utah are starting this quarter Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:

















                                                    Materion and Longstanding Beryllium Hydroxide Customer Complete Long-term Supply Agreement
                                                


                                                    Business Wire – 
                                                    10:17 AM ET 05/16/2017
                                                


Materion Corporation (MTRN) announced today that it has signed an agreement with a longstanding customer for a long-term supply of beryllium hydroxide material. Commenting on the agreement, Jugal Vijayvargiya, Materion President and Chief Executive Officer, said, We are excited to sign a long-term agreement and are especially pleased to resume regular shipments this quarter to a valued customer.

















                                                    Materion Expands Alumina Ceramic Material Offering with Introduction of Durox® 98
                                                


                                                    Business Wire – 
                                                    3:20 PM ET 05/04/2017
                                                


Materion Corporation (MTRN) has introduced Durox® 98 to its Durox family of alumina ceramic materials. The Companys alumina product offerings meet the demands of niche applications for high-purity ceramic material. Materion (MTRN) developed Durox 98 in response to customer demand for materials and applications that do not require the premium performance of beryllium oxide.

















                                                    BRIEF-Materion Corporation declared Q2 dividend of $0.10/shr, a 5 pct increase
                                                


                                                    Reuters – 
                                                    11:39 AM ET 05/03/2017
                                                


Materion Corp (MTRN). * Materion Corporation (MTRN) increases quarterly cash dividend. * Materion Corp (MTRN) - declared a Q2 2017 dividend of $0.10 per share of common stock, an increase of $0.005 per share, or approximately 5% Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:

















                                                    Materion Corporation Increases Quarterly Cash Dividend
                                                


                                                    Business Wire – 
                                                    11:36 AM ET 05/03/2017
                                                


Materion Corporation (MTRN) announced today that its Board of Directors declared a second quarter 2017 dividend of $0.10 per share of common stock, an increase of $0.005 per share, or approximately 5%. The dividend is payable on June 2, 2017 to shareholders of record at the close of business on May 17, 2017.

















                                                    BRIEF-Materion Corp sees 2017 capex about $25 mln - $30 mln - SEC filing
                                                


                                                    Reuters – 
                                                    1:32 PM ET 04/28/2017
                                                


Materion Corp (MTRN): * Sees 2017 capex approximately $25 million - $30 million - SEC filing Source text: Further company coverage:

















                                                    BRIEF-Materion Corp posts Q1 EPS of $0.15
                                                


                                                    Reuters – 
                                                    8:14 AM ET 04/28/2017
                                                


Materion Corp (MTRN). * Materion (MTRN) corporation reports first quarter 2017 financial results and confirms outlook for 2017. * Q1 adjusted earnings per share $0.29. * Q1 earnings per share $0.15. * Q1 sales $240.7 million versus $235.5 million.

















                                                    Materion Corporation Reports First Quarter 2017 Financial Results and Confirms Outlook for 2017
                                                


                                                    Business Wire – 
                                                    7:59 AM ET 04/28/2017
                                                


Materion Corporation (MTRN) today reported first quarter 2017 financial results. FIRST QUARTER 2017 RESULTS Net sales for the first quarter of 2017 were $240.7 million, compared to net sales of $235.5 million for the first quarter of 2016. Operating profit for the first quarter of 2017 was $3.4 million versus $7.5 million for the first quarter of the prior year.












